
PREREQUISITES

 * ocamlfind
 * prerequisites for OCaml as given in the file INSTALL

1/ $ ./configure \
      [-prefix <path/to/install/dir>] \
	  [-ocamlpath <dir/ocamlc/and/so/lives/in>] # defaults to the directory of `ocamlrun'

2/ Tell ocamlfind to ignore ocaml's original objects in doubt:
   $ export OCAMLFIND_IGNORE_DUPS_IN=`ocamlc -where`

3/ ./build/mkmyocamlbuild_config.sh

4/ Build _build/ecaml and _build/ecamlc:
   $ make ecamlc; make ecaml

5/ build an error reporting plugin:
   $ ocamlbuild easyadd/htmlErrorReport.cmo
